OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrakeford surprised at     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flevel of anger over 20mph  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, First Minister Mark Drakeford has      
OL,6, defended Wales' 20mph speed limit days 
OL,7, before he steps down.                  
OL,9,FMr Drakeford said he was surprised by  
OL,10,Fthe level of opposition and anger the  
OL,11,Fnew limit provoked.                    
OL,13,FHowever, he said he has chosen to      
OL,14,Ftackle "difficult and challenging"     
OL,15,Fissues, not spend his time "sitting    
OL,16,Fback and doing the easy things".       
OL,18,FOn Saturday, either Jeremy Miles or    
OL,19,FVaughan Gething will be announced as Mr
OL,20,FDrakeford's successor.                 
